prop.name: provider
prop.desc: The service provider, service operator, or service performer; the goods producer. Another party (a seller) may offer those services or goods on behalf of the provider. A provider may also serve as the seller.

prop.name: trackingUrl
prop.desc: Tracking url for the parcel delivery.

prop.name: hasDeliveryMethod
prop.desc: Method used for delivery or shipping.

prop.name: deliveryStatus
prop.desc: New entry added as the package passes through each leg of its journey (from shipment to final delivery).

prop.name: carrier
prop.desc: 'carrier' is an out-dated term indicating the 'provider' for parcel delivery and flights.

prop.name: partOfOrder
prop.desc: The overall order the items in this delivery were included in.

prop.name: expectedArrivalFrom
prop.desc: The earliest date the package may arrive.

prop.name: expectedArrivalUntil
prop.desc: The latest date the package may arrive.
